transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Haan ji.
Customer: Haan haan ji sir Kavita Rawat this side from IndiaMART. Good morning sir. Abhi aapne customer care pe call kiya tha sir account se related bataiye sir.
Customer: Kya kuch kya bataunga inquiry nahi aa rahi hai mere ko band karwana hai aur mera refund kar do bas wahi kaam hai.
Executive: Inquiry aapke hisab se kaise nahi aa rahi hai sir main dekh rahi hu inquiry.
Customer: Nahi aa rahi hai matlab panch panch inquiry kya kaam ki dilwane ka matlab kya fir.
Executive: Sir dilwane ka matlab kya?
Customer: Abhi wo aap bolo waisa nahi hota hai business mein dala hua paisa refund hona chahiye yaar aap log bologe itne aa gaye to hum hum bhi aaye hai na aapko paisa hi diya hai na to fir hamara work nahi hoga to hum kya karenge.
Executive: Sir kal aap keh rahe the aapko business aa raha hai sab theek hai inquiry.
Customer: Kal bola tha kab bola.
Executive: Kal hi to aapne bola tha hamari baat hui thi jab.
Customer: Are bhai kal tumhare sath baat hi nahi hui kyu jhoot bol rahe ho subah morning morning mein yaar.
Executive: Sir kal hum logo ki baat nahi hui. Sir IndiaMART se Kavita Rawat baat kar rahi hu main.
Customer: Haan kaun yaar. Kaun hai? Jhoot baat ki didi. Haan. To tere team ki to business achcha ho raha hai.
Executive: Aapko bola to tha inquiry nahi aa raha hai aisa kal.
Customer: Sir maine inquiries ka aapka khud se check karke aapko.
Customer: Nahi to mujhe hai na inquiry chahiye 10 se 15 aayegi na to hi mujhe karna hai warna nikal deta hu main.
Executive: Pehle aap apna naam bataye sir ek hi number se do log baat karte hai to main bhi confuse. Haan do log baat karte hai to aapko kal bola tha to abhi aap kyu bol rahe ho business achcha aa raha hai aisa kisne bola.
Executive: Kyunki mera kal hi discussion hua hai na sir. Haan to us wo to mana bol raha hai usne aisa nahi bola hai to fir.
Customer: Sir abhi aapne bola kal baat nahi hui.
Executive: Madam aap hai na aap hai na pehle to mujhe inquiry plus karke do business.
Customer: Sir inquiry achcha ho ya bura ho jo bhi ho mujhe nahi pata hai. Mere hath mein jo hai agar aapke pass buylead aapke nahi aa rahi hai.
Customer: Nahi hai to mujhe aap change ho jaiye change ho jaiye manager okay madam. Last time mera account slow ja raha hai mere ko nahi karna hai work is tarah mere ko work wapis chahiye paisa.
Executive: Agar aapko account manager change karna hai to ho jayega sir usme koi problem nahi hai.
Customer: Work nahi ho raha hai madam aap log ghar mein baithe ho bas aapko aisa hai dikhao na to fir nahi hai to lag raha hai to aisa.
Executive: Nahi nahi nahi sir aap aise baat nahi kar sakte pehli baat to aap chilla ke baat nahi kar sakte sir.
Customer: Aap account pe profile check karke mujhe dikhao yaha pe aapka growth hua. Sir main profile check hi kar rahi hu theek hai main aapke regular aapke team ke sath connection mein hu ye aisa nahi hai ki main connected nahi hu agar main connection mein nahi hoti to mahine mein char call nahi kar sakti na sir.
Executive: Nahi nahi ye yaar ye sab galat cheeze mat rakho aur sahi work karke batao aur ye galat cheez hai yaar nahi inquiry mil rahi hai dhang se aur nahi aapka work dikh raha hai mujhe.
Customer: Main ek bas kya chahte ho aap kya work karu main isme inquiries.
Executive: Nahi inquiry aayegi to hum kya karenge account hum profile rakh rahe hai.
Executive: Main check nahi kar sakti hu na. Profile check nahi kar sakte ho to fir kya kar sakte ho sirf bas account call kar do main main aapko kya bata rahi hu main kya kar sakti hu wo suniye.
Customer: Bas sirf itna hi bol sakte ho call karke sir business kaisa chal raha hai wo kaisa chal raha hai baat khatam ho gayi utne mein.
Executive: Baat karte ho yaar.
Executive: To fir wahi to aap bolte rehte ho bas inquiry mere hath mein nahi hai to hum kya kare usme.
Customer: Pehle to aap sir meri bhi baat suniye theek hai aap agar bolte rahenge to main nahi bata paungi aapko kuch bhi nahi samjha paungi.
Customer: Mere ko okay chalo abhi rakho yaar madam sorry.
